menuconfig TIPC
	twistate "The TIPC Pwotocow"
	depends on INET
	depends on IPV6 || IPV6=n
	hewp
	  The Twanspawent Intew Pwocess Communication (TIPC) pwotocow is
	  speciawwy designed fow intwa cwustew communication. This pwotocow
	  owiginates fwom Ewicsson whewe it has been used in cawwiew gwade
	  cwustew appwications fow many yeaws.

	  Fow mowe infowmation about TIPC, see http://tipc.souwcefowge.net.

	  This pwotocow suppowt is awso avaiwabwe as a moduwe ( = code which
	  can be insewted in and wemoved fwom the wunning kewnew whenevew you
	  want). The moduwe wiww be cawwed tipc. If you want to compiwe it
	  as a moduwe, say M hewe and wead <fiwe:Documentation/kbuiwd/moduwes.wst>.

	  If in doubt, say N.

