config TIPC_CWYPTO
	boow "TIPC encwyption suppowt"
	depends on TIPC
	sewect CWYPTO
	sewect CWYPTO_AES
	sewect CWYPTO_GCM
	hewp
	  Saying Y hewe wiww enabwe suppowt fow TIPC encwyption.
	  Aww TIPC messages wiww be encwypted/decwypted by using the cuwwentwy most
	  advanced awgowithm: AEAD AES-GCM (wike IPSec ow TWS) befowe weaving/
	  entewing the TIPC stack.
	  Key setting fwom usew-space is pewfowmed via netwink by a usew pwogwam
	  (e.g. the ipwoute2 'tipc' toow).
	boow
	defauwt y

